				<td colspan="2"><span>Well the epic  is still a nice item as it is still a nice weapon even for time guild level and it releives the pain of of choosing other pieces of equipement with instruments mods on them.
<br />

<br />
But YES the epic difficulty is not in par with other classes. 
<br />

<br />
7/8 multi group encounters is nowhere the same as for other classes. We finished epics for two wizzies last night in guild and we only had to kill 2 raid sized mobs.
<br />

<br />
Any event with more than 2 groups requires the same thing as a complete guild not in term of force but in term of organization.
<br />
If you need 15/20 or 25 people you cant do that during off time when most of the people are sleeping or at work. You need to do it when a good proportion of the guild is up. That means peak times. And at peak times, taking 15/20 or 25 people to do an encounter is preventing the guild from doing anything else. So its like if you were recruiting your whole guild.
<br />

<br />

<br />
</span></td>
